{"tid":2428382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"據報英國政府正投資到科技新創公司","createTime":"2021-03-01T13:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T08:50:37.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6ebb1ec44b9ba6b8e7c38c1652f253ac2dc381","tid":2428382,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T13:26:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gwWljZO9PDpFSO9fCifzTw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC4wNDk1MzU2MDM3MTUy/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/c5VrNLFiEEayj3wPkR2eDw--~B/aD00MzA3O3c9NjQ2MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/engadget_hk_378/3c10c15c6574c82976b84e5ba41e5a16\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgwWljZO9PDpFSO9fCifzTw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MC4wNDk1MzU2MDM3MTUy%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fc5VrNLFiEEayj3wPkR2eDw--~B%2FaD00MzA3O3c9NjQ2MDthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fengadget_hk_378%2F3c10c15c6574c82976b84e5ba41e5a16&h=577a210e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n世界各國都以不同方式來大力投資到科技產業，金融時報獲悉英國政府更會透過成立新基金「Future Fund: Breakthrough」，會特別針對科技新創公司投資，金額會達 3.75 億英鎊。如此的做法，相信能協助英國科企的發展。據消息人士透露，每項投資都將以千萬英鎊計，並由私募基金協助配對，而大型科企的投資佔比就會相對少。<br />\n<br />\n預計英國政府會在 3 月 3 日的財政預算案上公表更多詳情，相信也會引起外界的不少關注，因為這算是拿著納稅人的錢去投資，那資金配對的方向又是否能公平對待？而且投資新創科企都涉及相對高的風險，人們又是否接受呢？當然，英國也能藉此防止自家新創技術被外來資金搶走，這也是未來基金的一個用途。"},{"pid":"60ab4302c5f4369245ac731b5a3702d076c878bb","tid":2428382,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d5ed51c95fe4d27fa101c1a60d2bb909be1161","tid":2428382,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"香港人可以為英國作出貢獻"},{"pid":"a869a27e02d3346237edadd4